ISIGUNGU esiphezulu somfelandawonye wezinyunyana iSouth African Federation of Trade Unions (Saftu), simise emsebenzini umengameli waso, iphini lakhe lesibili, umgcinimafa nephini likanobhala. Laba abane okunguMnuz Mac Chavalala, Thabo Matsose, Motshwari Lecogo noPhakedi Moleko, bamiswe ngoMgqibelo, emva komhlangano wesigungu seSaftu. Bamiswe ngezinsolo zokwakha itulo lokumisa emsebenzini uNobhala jikelele uMnuz Zwelinzima Vavi, ababemsola ngokuxhaphaza imali yeSaftu. Isenzo sabo kuthiwa sidicilela phansi isuthunzi seSaftu nokusebenzisa budlabha amandla ezikhundla abaziphethe. Isinqumo sithathwe emhlanganweni wezinsuku ezintathu wesigungu esiphezulu seSaftu ophothulwe ngoMgqibelo. Isigungu esiphezulu sithi akulandelwanga uMthethosisekelo weSaftu ngesikhathi kumiswa uVavi emsebezini okuyisinqumo esiguquliwe kwase kuvotelwa ukumiswa kwalaba abane.  